{"tid":1887991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"畢馬威: 政府應向香港巿民派 1 萬元採取大膽行動刺激經濟！","createTime":"2020-02-20T02:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T04:16:59.000Z","uid":63113,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e85e962fb1b2317292bc66adc5cbf8c291f039da","tid":1887991,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a2905835fe25debad7da0d120cc51c36a80204","tid":1887991,"uid":63113,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"受新型冠狀病毒肺炎（武漢肺炎 COVID-19）疫情影響，不少行業都大受打擊，社會亦有聲音，仍為政府應該「派錢」。日前會計師事務所畢馬威發表《2020/21 年度香港財政預算案回顧及前瞻》，闡述對香港 2019/20 財政年度的財政預測，認為香港政府應動用充足的財政儲備，來刺激陷入衰退的經濟，包括向每位市民提供 10,000 港元補助金。<br />\n<br />\n畢馬威表示，預計香港將在 2019-2020 財年錄得 15 年來首次赤字，綜合預算赤字為 477 億港元，認為政府應在 2 月 26 日發布預算時，採取大膽行動，除了保護和加強本地支持計劃，亦應避免增加稅收，不宜削減開支。<br />\n<br />\n畢馬威建議向每名 18 至 69 歲香港永久性居民派發 1 萬港元電子消費券，特定用於一般消費、飲食和消閒娛樂，70 歲以上居民可透過高齡津貼收取 1 萬港元現金，刺激本地經濟。其他建議還包括支持在職父母，為住宅物業的租金支出提供稅務減免等。<br />\n<br />\n畢馬威認為，跟 2003 年 SARS 危機相比，現時香港的財政狀況更建康，應立即採取措施刺激經濟。根據政府公告，截至 12 月 31 日，香港的財政儲備約為 1.12 萬億港元。不過香港財政司司長陳茂波也曾表示，「為確保公共財政的穩定，未來在考慮新增的開支，尤其是經常性開支時，必須更注意財政上的可持續性，量入為出」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sme.hket.com/article/2569211/%E7%95%A2%E9%A6%AC%E5%A8%81:%20%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%87%89%E5%90%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B7%BF%E6%B0%91%E6%B4%BE%201%20%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%20%20%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E5%A4%A7%E8%86%BD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsme.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2569211%2F%25E7%2595%25A2%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%25A8%2581%3A%2520%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2590%2591%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B7%25BF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25B4%25BE%25201%2520%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%2520%2520%25E6%258E%25A1%25E5%258F%2596%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2586%25BD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2588%25BA%25E6%25BF%2580%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5OzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=4983b5f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://sme.hket.com/article/2569211/%E7%95%A2%E9%A6%AC%E5%A8%81:%20%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%87%89%E5%90%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B7%BF%E6%B0%91%E6%B4%BE%201%20%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%20%20%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E5%A4%A7%E8%86%BD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F</a>"},{"pid":"460a507334bb3ceef1b5cafd8ada78f7bf70f87e","tid":1887991,"uid":11067,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"行政費300億，填form一年，派足兩年"},{"pid":"aead10bd1a50470fc78eeecf317a91b793e12a85","tid":1887991,"uid":230911,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e85e962fb1b2317292bc66adc5cbf8c291f039da","tid":1887991,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:40:35.000Z","msg":"不如再大膽，將庫房既錢分晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d3b2fbd201277393a946c437f69bae1e2f7ddd","tid":1887991,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:41:17.000Z","msg":"KPMG係咪冇生意所以黃咗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d850058f77a874585f9e75cc804357b39ea7b62","tid":1887991,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aead10bd1a50470fc78eeecf317a91b793e12a85","tid":1887991,"uid":230911,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e85e962fb1b2317292bc66adc5cbf8c291f039da","tid":1887991,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:40:35.000Z","msg":"不如再大膽，將庫房既錢分晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma